1
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:33,130
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:36,190
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:36,830 --> 00:01:40,330
[Virtue and Merit in Equal Splendor]

4
00:01:45,259 --> 00:01:47,240
My mother was born a noblewoman.

5
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:49,990
But she ended up a prisoner
in Lingya Tower.

6
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:53,610
Then that bastard Meng Shuo defiled her.

7
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,720
That was how she had me.

8
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,759
The other women in prison looked after us.

9
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:03,240
They taught me to read and fight.

10
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:07,260
But I could only watch them
participate in the death match,

11
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,479
dying one by one,

12
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,639
and I was powerless to help.

13
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,560
Master.

14
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,600
It's all in the past now.

15
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,840
Let's not talk about it tonight.

16
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,320
Here.

17
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,510
Okay.

18
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,200
Cheers.

19
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,040
Long trapped in a cage,

20
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:35,480
now free in nature again.

21
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,300
If Lingya Tower didn't exist,

22
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:41,700
I'd really want to stay here
with you forever.

23
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,079
Then tonight, let's pretend

24
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,079
none of it exists.

25
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,570
No tower.

26
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,560
No cage.

27
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,950
Just wine.

28
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,640
Just rabbit.

29
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,700
Just master and disciple.

30
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,490
Then eat up.

31
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,240
Maybe this meal

32
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,720
is the last peace we'll get.

33
00:03:19,010 --> 00:03:19,579
Here.

34
00:03:24,850 --> 00:03:25,650
Yummy.

35
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,320
Yummy.

36
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,360
It's so yummy.

37
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:29,829
Master.

38
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,710
If you hadn't learned martial arts,

39
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:33,040
you could've been a cook

40
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,320
and fed me for life.

41
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,600
Slow down.

42
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:38,560
Don't choke.

43
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,880
Look at you.

44
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,320
Master.

45
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:44,200
Do you remember
when you first came to our home

46
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,840
and had your first meal?

47
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,800
It's been so long.

48
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:51,040
You still remember?

49
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,320
How could I forget?

50
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,490
You were badly wounded.

51
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,700
We cared for you for so long.

52
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:59,010
We nearly thought you'd never wake up.

53
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,400
But after you woke up,

54
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,780
the first thing you did

55
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,440
was ask for meat.

56
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,960
Back then I risked my life
escaping the tower.

57
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,320
It was the first time I'd seen the world.

58
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,880
Thankfully I met you all.

59
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,930
Rabbit.

60
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:44,630
You...

61
00:05:14,730 --> 00:05:17,330
My mother made this rabbit
specially for you.

62
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,530
Can I become your disciple?

63
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,740
I like rabbit too.

64
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:26,680
Can you teach me how to catch one?

65
00:05:31,820 --> 00:05:34,080
Look, my braiding isn't that bad, right?

66
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:39,310
Master, when will you start teaching me?

67
00:05:39,530 --> 00:05:41,860
When did I agree to
take you as my disciple?

68
00:05:42,530 --> 00:05:44,680
Since I combed your hair for you,

69
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:46,490
please think about it, Master.

70
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,460
I've never taken a disciple.

71
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:49,290
I don't know how to teach.

72
00:05:49,290 --> 00:05:51,460
I've never had a master either.

73
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:53,560
We can look out for each other.

74
00:05:55,450 --> 00:05:56,580
I'll think about it.

75
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,630
I'll take that as a yes.

76
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,520
Let's pinky swear.

77
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,560
No backing out.

78
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,120
Do you know

79
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,520
how much pain

80
00:06:05,910 --> 00:06:07,550
it takes to gain such skills?

81
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,920
Master.

82
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:36,320
Master, teach me your best martial arts.

83
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:38,450
I want to avenge my parents.

84
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,880
Things have been hard

85
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,960
for you lately.

86
00:08:03,890 --> 00:08:04,690
Not at all.

87
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,540
If it weren't for you, Master,

88
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:11,720
I don't know how I would've kept going.

89
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,640
I made this for you, Master.

90
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:23,410
I call it filigree bangle.

91
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,600
Someday, when you wear it,

92
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:28,500
we'll storm Lingya Tower together.

93
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:29,680
We'll be unstoppable

94
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,480
and nothing can stand in our way.

95
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,090
Lingya Tower is full of danger.

96
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:41,559
I can't let you risk your life with me.

97
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:44,420
How could I just watch you
go in alone, risk your life

98
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:45,590
and do nothing?

99
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,320
Then you'll have to.

100
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,240
I have my own plan.

101
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,960
Master.

102
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,180
You said it yourself.

103
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,530
Lingya Tower is extremely dangerous.

104
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:59,460
One more person means better odds.

105
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:03,880
Besides, if a sinful place
like Lingya Tower

106
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,900
isn't destroyed soon,

107
00:09:05,930 --> 00:09:08,370
more women will fall into it,

108
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,640
becoming playthings
for the rich and powerful,

109
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,570
and living a life worse than death.

110
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,950
Master. Master.

111
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:18,200
Just admit it this once.

112
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,440
Admit that you need me.

113
00:09:22,250 --> 00:09:23,250
Please.

114
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,840
Fine.

115
00:09:31,970 --> 00:09:32,930
But

116
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,270
you have to listen to me.

117
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:41,600
Yanzhi.

118
00:09:43,190 --> 00:09:45,170
Actually, you don't have to do this.

119
00:09:45,170 --> 00:09:46,010
Burn it.

120
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,880
Burn this place to ashes.

121
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:51,360
Then there'll be no turning back.

122
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,400
I know you're set on revenge.

123
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,700
But your mother is already...

124
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,400
If anything happens to you...

125
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:57,850
I...

126
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:58,680
Master.

127
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,640
In this world,

128
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,040
other than you,

129
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:07,740
I have nothing left to hold on to.

130
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:14,550
[Virtue and Merit in Equal Splendor]

131
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:23,460
Yanzhi.

132
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:24,560
Going to Lingya Tower

133
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,880
will definitely be dangerous.

134
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:28,080
You will enter with me
disguised as a mute servant.

135
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,480
We'll split up,

136
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,340
so I may not be able to protect you.

137
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:32,780
Be careful at every step.

138
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:35,180
Don't worry, Master.

139
00:10:36,070 --> 00:10:37,710
I can take care of myself.

140
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:46,640
Hyah!

141
00:10:47,770 --> 00:10:48,220
Hyah!

142
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:48,730
Hyah!

143
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:09,680
Wujiu.

144
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,320
It's late.

145
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,920
What are you still doing here?

146
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,140
Tower Master.

147
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:22,210
The Lantern Festival is coming up.

148
00:11:22,210 --> 00:11:24,230
I was ordered to
select the female prisoners,

149
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:25,490
so I dare not slack off.

150
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:27,730
Tower Master.

151
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:28,930
Hei Ya asks to see you.

152
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,450
Be thorough.

153
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:34,010
No mistakes.

154
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,360
Yes, Tower Master.

155
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,290
I'll go keep an eye on Hei Ya.

156
00:11:45,290 --> 00:11:46,010
You stay here

157
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:46,850
and continue the operation.

158
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:47,330
Yes.

159
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:48,930
Be careful, Master.

160
00:11:58,620 --> 00:11:59,620
Stop right there!

161
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:18,990
You got out.

162
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,600
Why come back?

163
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:36,740
Getting the antidote wasn't enough?

164
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,560
You came back to kill Hei Ya.

165
00:12:39,290 --> 00:12:41,800
How bold of you.

166
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:43,310
You knew?

167
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:45,040
Did you really think

168
00:12:45,700 --> 00:12:48,420
that your plans with Zhuang Wujiu

169
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,520
could fool everyone?

170
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:55,810
If the Tower Master
and I hadn't shown mercy,

171
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:58,860
you never would've reached
the fourth floor.

172
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:01,940
Don't act like you're so righteous,

173
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:04,600
as if that could wash away your sins.

174
00:13:05,030 --> 00:13:06,110
Enough talk.

175
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,160
Come on.

176
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:35,490
Qi.

177
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:37,840
Nan Yanzhi.

178
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,960
You're alive.

179
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:42,450
Thank goodness.

180
00:13:45,430 --> 00:13:46,790
I missed you so much.

181
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:50,420
Qi, you can talk?

182
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,520
My lord.

183
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:04,720
The girls serving you tonight
have all entered the tower.

184
00:14:09,230 --> 00:14:10,800
Looks like the real show

185
00:14:10,830 --> 00:14:12,590
is about to begin.

186
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:45,980
Zhuang Wujiu.

187
00:15:46,010 --> 00:15:49,360
How do you like the show
I arranged for you?

